stimulus:
For this phase you will see two similar images side by side on the screen I want you to tell us which of the items you have seen before in any of the previous sets of images.

If you have only seen the image on the left you will press the 'L' key on your keyboard.

If you have only seen the image on the right you will press the 'R' key on your keyboard.

If you have previously seen both of the images you will press the 'B' key on your keyboard.

If you have not seen either image you will press the 'N' key on your keyboard.

Press any key to begin.
